data.description:
Welcome Home!  This hard to find, move-in-ready 2-bedroom 1-bathroom condo is just what you've been looking for!  Walk into the spacious main living area.  Beautiful floors throughout the living/dining/kitchen.  Bright & open concept.  Kitchen boasts black/stainless steel appliances.  Updated kitchen.  Sleek subway tile backsplash.  Main floor laundry.  Upper-level leads to the bedrooms/bathroom.  Bathroom is equipped with double sinks.  Windows replaced in 2020.  Professionally cleaned carpeting in the bedrooms.
Patio is private & fenced.  
Don't miss your opportunity to view this gem!
